ActNorth American Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act
SubjectNAFTA - EXCHANGE OF LETTERS - Annex 401 (Specific Rules of Origin)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the EXCHANGE OF LETTERS constituting an Agreement between the Government of Canada, the Government of the UNITED STATES OF AMERICA and the Government of the UNITED MEXICAN STATES, amending Annex 401 of the North American Free Trade Agreement, to liberalize the rules of origin for a variety of products.
